# containsTimeRange(_:)

**Instance Method**

Returns a Boolean value that indicates whether the time range contains another time range.

## Declaration

```swift
func containsTimeRange(_ range: CMTimeRange) -> Bool
```

## Parameters

- **range**: The time range to test for inclusion.

## Return Value

[doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Swift/true] if time range contains `range`; otherwise, [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Swift/false].

## Finding Elements

- **containsTime(_:)**: Returns a Boolean value that indicates whether the time range contains a time.
